The paper discusses the use of deep learning models in healthcare applications, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques, which are covered by cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) respectively. Additionally, the paper uses ensemble learning techniques, which can be categorized under cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
